02:06:47.040 --> 02:06:48.200
for a secret group

02:06:48.200 --> 02:06:49.320
that used to meet there.

02:06:49.480 --> 02:06:50.020
It was called

02:06:50.020 --> 02:06:50.940
the Nassau Group

02:06:50.940 --> 02:06:51.800
and it included

02:06:51.800 --> 02:06:53.240
the elite of the elite,

02:06:53.440 --> 02:06:54.380
industrialists

02:06:54.380 --> 02:06:56.060
like Eldridge Reeves Johnson,

02:06:56.380 --> 02:06:57.700
and even the inspiration

02:06:57.700 --> 02:06:58.780
for James Bond

02:06:58.780 --> 02:07:00.320
and Churchill's super spy,

02:07:00.480 --> 02:07:01.460
William Stevenson,

02:07:01.580 --> 02:07:02.880
who helped form the CIA.

02:07:03.280 --> 02:07:04.600
So maybe Tim and Townsend

02:07:04.600 --> 02:07:05.560
are part of a secret

02:07:05.560 --> 02:07:06.380
time travel group.

02:07:06.480 --> 02:07:07.080
Who knows?

02:07:07.320 --> 02:07:08.440
But it is interesting

02:07:08.440 --> 02:07:09.460
that Taylor seems

02:07:09.460 --> 02:07:11.300
